cast.overview: Tired of being locked in a reptile house where humans gawk at them like they are monsters, a ragtag group of Australia’s deadliest creatures plot an escape from their zoo to the Outback, a place where they’ll fit in without being judged.
cast.title: Back to the Outback

details.biography: Aislinn Derbez (born 18 March 1987) is a Mexican actress and model. She is the daughter of actors Eugenio Derbez and Gabriela Michel. Derbez began her career as a model at age 15, combined  with studies of performing and visual arts in New York for three years, then played several small roles in films until she became a breakthrough star.
details.name: Aislinn Derbez
